             <del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e391__Start"/>&amp;<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e391__End"/> my friends <lb n="c57-0079__main__3"/>unconscious of the existence of their <lb n="c57-0079__main__4"/>enemy &amp; unprotected from his attacks <lb n="c57-0079__main__5"/>exasperated as he might be by my <w ana="start"/>depar<lb n="c57-0079__main__6"/>ture<w ana="end"/> – But then he had promised to <lb n="c57-0079__main__7"/>follow me every where &amp; might <lb n="c57-0079__main__8"/>he not accompany me to England–the <lb n="c57-0079__main__9"/>thought was dreadful in itself but <lb n="c57-0079__main__10"/>soothing inasmuch as my friends would <lb n="c57-0079__main__11"/>be in safety. <del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e418__Start"/><add loc="c57-0079__main__d1e419__Start"/><metamark function="displacement" xml:id="c57-0079.02">X</metamark><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__Start"/><addSpan hand="#pbs" spanTo="#c57-0079.03"/> <lb n="c57-0079__left_margin__1"/>the thought of <lb n="c57-0079__left_margin__2"/>the possibility<add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e429__Start"/><metamark function="sequence">5</metamark><add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e429__End"/> <lb n="c57-0079__left_margin__3"/>of the reverse <lb n="c57-0079__left_margin__4"/>must have <lb n="c57-0079__left_margin__5"/>been dreadful<anchor xml:id="c57-0079.03"/><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__End"/><add loc="c57-0079__main__d1e419__End"/><del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e418__End"/> The thoughts
             occurred <lb n="c57-0079__main__12"/>rapidly to me &amp; I answered my <w ana="start"/>fa<lb n="c57-0079__main__13"/>ther<w ana="end"/> with eagerness that I should <lb n="c57-0079__main__14"/>be delighted to visit <del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e453__Start"/>Engl<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e453__End"/> England <lb n="c57-0079__main__15"/>with Clerval and that <del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e458__Start"/>travel<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e458__End"/> the <lb n="c57-0079__main__16"/>idea of travelling was inchanting to <lb n="c57-0079__main__17"/>me.<milestone unit="tei:p"/><delSpan rend="vertical_line" spanTo="#c57-0079.04"/> <lb n="c57-0079__main__18"/>Your <del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e471__Start"/>journey<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e471__End"/> travels, said
             my <lb n="c57-0079__main__19"/>father, will occupy the space of <lb n="c57-0079__main__20"/>two years– on your return you <lb n="c57-0079__main__21"/><del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e480__Start"/>shall be united to your cousin<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e480__End"/><anchor xml:id="c57-0079.04"/><milestone unit="tei:p"/> <lb n="c57-0079__main__22"/>Our plan was soon arranged. <lb n="c57-0079__main__23"/>I should travel to Strasburgh where <lb n="c57-0079__main__24"/>Clerval would join me &amp; we <lb n="c57-0079__main__25"/>should proceed down the Rhine <lb n="c57-0079__main__26"/>together.<del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e496__Start"/><add loc="c57-0079__main__d1e497__Start"/><unclear reason="illegible">tow</unclear><add loc="c57-0079__main__d1e497__End"/><del loc="c57-0079__main__d1e496__End"/> Some short time would <lb n="c57-0079__main__27"/>be spent in the towns of Holland <lb n="c57-0079__main__28"/>&amp; many months in England. We were <lb n="c57-0079__main__29"/>to return by france &amp; it was <w ana="start"/>sup<lb n="c57-0079__main__30"/>posed<w ana="end"/> that this tour would occupy <lb n="c57-0079__main__31"/>the space of two years. My father <lb n="c57-0079__main__32"/>pleased himself with the reflection <lb n="c57-0079__main__33"/>that I should be united to <w ana="start"/>Eliza<lb n="c57-0079__main__34"/>beth<w ana="end"/> immediately on my return<anchor xml:id="c57-0079.01"/><zone loc="c57-0079__main__End"/><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__Start"/> <add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e530__Start"/><metamark function="sequence">3</metamark><add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e530__End"/><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__End"/><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__Start"/> <add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e535__Start"/><metamark>X</metamark><add loc="c57-0079__left_margin__d1e535__End"/><zone loc="c57-0079__left_margin__End"/><surface xml:id="ox-ms_abinger_c57-0079__End"/>
    <surface xml:id="ox-ms_abinger_c57-0080__Start"/><graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ms_abinger_c57/ms_abinger_c57-0080.jp2"/><zone loc="c57-0080__main__Start"/><delSpan rend="vertical_line" spanTo="#c57-0080.01"/> <lb n="c57-0080__main__1"/>to Geneva. These two years, said he, will pass <lb n="c57-0080__main__2"/>swiftly and it will be the last delay that will <lb n="c57-0080__main__3"/>oppose itself to your happiness. How do I long <lb n="c57-0080__main__4"/>for that time when we shall be all <lb n="c57-0080__main__5"/>united and <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e555__Start"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e557__Start"/><metamark function="insert">^</metamark><add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e557__End"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e561__Start"/>neither<add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e561__End"/>
          <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e555__End"/> hopes or fears <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e565__Start"/>
             <del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e567__Start"/>will<del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e567__End"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e570__Start"/><metamark function="insert">^</metamark><add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e570__End"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e574__Start"/>arise<add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e574__End"/>
          <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e565__End"/> destroy our <lb n="c57-0080__main__6"/>domestic felicity. <milestone unit="tei:p"/>
           <lb n="c57-0080__main__7"/>I am content, I replied, with your  <lb n="c57-0080__main__8"/>arrangement. By that time we shall <lb n="c57-0080__main__9"/>both have become wiser &amp; I hope happier <lb n="c57-0080__main__10"/>than we are now. I sigh<mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e591__Start"/>
             <mdel>t</mdel>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e596__Start"/>e<add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e596__End"/>
          <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e591__End"/>d. But my father <lb n="c57-0080__main__11"/>kindly forebore to question me concerning <lb n="c57-0080__main__12"/>the cause of my dejection. He hoped that <lb n="c57-0080__main__13"/>new scenes &amp; the amusement of travelling <lb n="c57-0080__main__14"/>would restore my tranquility<add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e609__Start"/><metamark>X</metamark><add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e609__End"/><anchor xml:id="c57-0080.01"/><milestone unit="tei:p"/> <lb n="c57-0080__main__15"/>It was in the latter end of August <lb n="c57-0080__main__16"/>that I departed to pass two years of exile. <lb n="c57-0080__main__17"/><del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e621__Start"/>M<del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e621__End"/> Elizabeth approved of the reasons of my <lb n="c57-0080__main__18"/>departure and only regretted that she <lb n="c57-0080__main__19"/>had not the same opportunities of <w ana="start"/>enlarg<lb n="c57-0080__main__20"/>ing<w ana="end"/> her experience &amp; cultivating her <lb n="c57-0080__main__21"/>understanding –She wept however as she <lb n="c57-0080__main__22"/>bade me farewell and entreated to return <lb n="c57-0080__main__23"/>happy &amp; tranquil. We all, said she, depend <lb n="c57-0080__main__24"/>upon you, &amp; if you are miserable <lb n="c57-0080__main__25"/>what must be our feelings?<milestone unit="tei:p"/> <lb n="c57-0080__main__26"/>I threw myself into the carriage <lb n="c57-0080__main__27"/>that was to conve<retrace cause="unclear">y</retrace> me away hardly <lb n="c57-0080__main__28"/>knowing <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e657__Start"/>
             <del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e659__Start"/>where<del loc="c57-0080__main__d1e659__End"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e662__Start"/><metamark function="insert">^</metamark><add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e662__End"/>
             <add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e666__Start"/>whither<add loc="c57-0080__main__d1e666__End"/>
          <mod loc="c57-0080__main__d1e657__End"/> I was going &amp; careless of <lb n="c57-0080__main__29"/>what was passing around. I remembered <lb n="c57-0080__main__30"/>only, and it was with a bitter anguish <lb n="c57-0080__main__31"/>that I reflected on it, to order that my <lb n="c57-0080__main__32"/>chemical instruments should be packed <lb n="c57-0080__main__33"/>to go with me. For I resolved to fulfil <lb n="c57-0080__main__34"/>my promise while abroard &amp; return if <lb n="c57-0080__main__35"/>possible a free man. Filled with<zone loc="c57-0080__main__End"/><zone loc="c57-0080__left_margin__Start"/> <metamark function="sequence">4</metamark><zone loc="c57-0080__left_margin__End"/><surface xml:id="ox-ms_abinger_c57-0080__End"/>
